{
  "title": "Bitter Crunchy Portuguese Sesame Burger",
  "description": "A unique burger featuring bitter greens, crunchy sesame seed buns, and a Mediterranean-inspired stir-fry, perfect for a festive Portuguese meal. This dish combines the flavors of Portugal with the crunch of sesame seeds and the bitterness of arugula.",
