  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "In a bowl, mix yeast, flour, salt, and sesame seeds. Gradually add water to form a dough.",
    "Knead dough for 10 minutes, then let rest for 1 hour.",
    "Divide dough into 4 equal pieces and shape into buns.",
    "Bake buns for 15-20 minutes, or until golden brown.",
    "In a pan, heat olive oil over medium heat. Add sliced sausage and cook until browned.",
    "Add red onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add arugula, olives, and feta cheese to the pan. Stir-fry for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Assemble burgers with cooked sausage, stir-fry, and sesame seed buns."
